<div>
  <h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:24px;line-height:1.2;color:#202020;">Your delivery settings need attention</h1>
  <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#57636c;">
    Hi <strong><%= vendorName %></strong>,
  </p>
  <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#57636c;">
    <strong><%= hiddenCount %></strong> of your self-fulfilled product<%= hiddenCount === 1 ? " is" : "s are" %> currently hidden from the Piessang storefront because your delivery settings are incomplete.
  </p>
  <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#57636c;">
    To make these products visible again, please add at least one of the following in your seller dashboard:
  </p>
  <ul style="margin:0 0 16px 18px;padding:0;color:#57636c;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;">
    <li>Local delivery</li>
    <li>Courier delivery</li>
    <li>Collection</li>
  </ul>
  <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#57636c;">
    Once your delivery settings are saved, the affected products can appear on the storefront again automatically.
  </p>
</div>
